, iOS, Android) as they go, but prior experience is not required. They must be located within ±2 hours of the Europe/Berlin time zone.</p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; border-style: initial; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.7; font-family: Roboto, HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: #444444; letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">Example tasks might include (we work on everything as a team):</p>\n<ul style=\"margin-bottom: 40px; margin-left: 20px; padding-left: 0px; border-style: initial; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto, HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #444444; letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">\n<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border-style: initial; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.7; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Add a list of current game tests to our Flutter App, for which you also need to implement the REST backend in our Rails app.</li>\n<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border-style: initial; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.7; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Hook up an external API to add sentiment information to our player videos.</li>\n<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border-style: initial; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.7; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Integrate a Python Tensorflow CNN into our Ruby video processing pipeline.</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; border-style: initial; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.7; font-family: Roboto, HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: #444444; letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">It would also be great if:</p>\n<ul style=\"margin-bottom: 40px; margin-left: 20px; padding-left: 0px; border-style: initial; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto, HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #444444; letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">\n<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border-style: initial; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.7; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">you have experience working on real-world web applications, through university projects or prior jobs</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; border-style: initial; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.7; font-family: Roboto, HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: #444444; letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-style: initial; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Perks</span></p>\n<ul style=\"margin-bottom: 40px; margin-left: 20px; padding-left: 0px; border-style: initial; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto, HelveticaNeue-Light, \'Helvetica Neue Light\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sa