 their brand’s e-commerce approach</p>\n<p>As we are growing quickly, Accorin is looking for a digital project manager with a strong background in the ecommerce space to join our team. The chosen candidate will be responsible for managing select ongoing maintenance and evolution projects, along with taking on new clients and projects. As PM you will ensure projects are delivered on time and within budget. This is a remote based, contractor position. Accorin prides itself on its exceptional client services. Above all else, we are looking for a project manager who is:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>A team leader</li>\n<li>Proactive and responsive</li>\n<li>An excellent communicator</li>\n</ul>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Ensure the full scope of the tasked project is delivered at a world class level.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Identify external and internal requests that fall outside the approved scope of the project.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Ensure the project budgets are attentively managed and maintained.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Budget status will be communicated to the client at regularly scheduled meetings over the course of the project.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Ensure the project schedules are attentively managed and maintained.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Schedule status will be communicated to the client at regularly scheduled meetings over the course of the project.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>You will lead and guide the team of developers, designers and QA engineers from the start of the project lifecycle to the end.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Set expectations for the team members. They should be 100% clear with regard to ownership and timing of deliverables.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>You will be expected to manage the client relationship over the course of the project.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Be attentive to what the client is communicating and set expectations for the client.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>Activities: </strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Project Kickoffs</li>\n<li>Setup New Projects and Associated Tools</li>\n<li>Manage Time Tracking</li>\n<li>Budget Management</li>\n<li>Estimating and Resourcing</li>\n<li>Schedule Generation and Management</li>\n<li>Issue and Task Management</li>\n<li>Meeting Management</li>\n<li>Status Updates</li>\n<li>Deliverable Reviews and Approvals</li>\n<li>Report to the Director of Project Management</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Minimum of 2 years of project management experience</li>\n<li>Experience in client management, presenting project updates to clients and managing expectations.</li>\n<li>Have previously worked on one or more of the following ecommerce platforms:</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Magento</p>\n<p>Shopify</p>\n<p>Big Commerce</p>\n<p>Laravel</p>\n<ul>\n<li>History of managing e commerce projects through the full lifecycle with a record of success</li>\n<li>Understanding of project management elementals and theory</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Agile and waterfall methodologies</p>\n<p>Sprint planning</p>\n<ul>\n<li>High level understanding of ecommerce related fields and processes including</li>\n</ul>\n<p>UI/UX principles</p>\n<p>Payment gateways</p>\n<p>Shipping and taxes</p>\n<p>Security protocols</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Preferably experience working with and managing offshore based development teams</li>\n</ul>\n<p> </p>\n','2021-07-07 18:39:49','USA Only','Wasserman','','remotive.io','2021-09-15 04:30:03','2021-09-15 04:30:03'),(17,'Senior Backend Developer','https://remotive.io/remote-jobs/software-dev/senior-backend-developer-767497','<p><strong>THE COMPANY</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Barkyn is improving the lives of pet families around the world with new magical e-commerce experience. </strong>We developed a platform that delivers health and happiness products and services in a comfortable and personalized way. Currently specialized in dogs, we provide subscription plans that include food, goodies, treats and a dedicated online vet.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>This way, <strong>we’re not only changing the pet market, but we’re also reshaping the way the