elopment, including HTML5, CSS3 &amp; PHP, Sass, Twig, and Javascript.</li>\n<li>Proven track record in building IT systems.</li>\n<li>Experience with REST API.</li>\n<li>Working knowledge of PHP frameworks such as Laravel.</li>\n<li>Experience with building restful JSON web services.</li>\n<li>User authentication and authorization between multiple systems, servers, and environments.</li>\n<li>Experience with MySQL and MongoDB.</li>\n<li>Experience with building large scale SaaS apps like CRM, CMS, and ERP.</li>\n<li>GIT.</li>\n<li>Docker.</li>\n<li>General knowledge of sockets (Swoole).</li>\n<li>English min. B2</li>\n</ul>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>15000 - 19000 PLN / monthly/ B2B (invoice without VAT)</li>\n<li>Stock options</li>\n<li>Long-term cooperation that gives stabilization</li>\n<li>Hardware</li>\n<li>A B2B contract that allows you to use IPBox</li>\n</ul>\n','2021-06-25 22:39:39','Poland only','IngeniousIO','','remotive.io','2021-09-15 04:30:03','2021-09-15 04:30:03'),(19,'Senior Backend Developer PHP API','https://remoteOK.io/remote-jobs/105933-remote-senior-backend-developer-php-api-flightradar24','Flightradar24 is looking for a PHP Backend Developer who is experienced with PHP web backend code and modern REST API development. You will play an important role in developing both the Flightradar24 website and API services, and your work will improve the experience of millions of users every day.\n\n**What youâll do**\n\n* Collaborate with a small team of developers and product owners on developing features for the Flightradar24 API services and websites\n* Deliver modern, testable and maintainable code using modern PHP7 (and soon PHP8), frameworks, and DevOps technologies\n* Be a lead contributor in the development of new API services\n* Participate in knowledge sharing and mentoring for other developers in your team\n\n**Who you are**\n\n* Extensive experience with modern REST API and web development in PHP7, preferably usi